<br>
Crystalline Spear - Ranger, Bard, Rogue, Warrior <br>
Dragon Bone Bracelet - Ranger, Paladin, Shadowknight, Bard, Monk, Rogue, Warrior <br>
Kayruuls Mystic Pouch - All/All<br>
McVaxius' Horn of War - Bard<br>
Runed Bolster Belt - Melee Classes Only<br>
Scimitar of the Mistwalker - Dru, Rng<br>
Staff of Forbidden Rites - Shaman Druid Cleric Paladin <br>
Tobrin's Mystical Eyepatch - Enc, Wiz, Mag, Nec, Clr, Dru, Shm (Not all/all - only pure wis or int casters on this) <br>
Warhammer of Divine Grace - Cleric<br>
Half of the Book of Scale - Paladins Only<br>
White Dragon Scale - Wiz, Enc, Mag, Nec, Clr, Dru, Shm, Pal, Shd, Ranger, Brd (Restricted to those who really use the Wisdom and Int) - This is used for the White Dragon Scale Cloak AND the Bard Epic<br>
<br>
This is based on &quot;use before profit&quot; and on &quot;you bleed, you roll.&quot; I realize not everyone will agree with it, but this is the system we will use on Vox. <br>
<br>
[Edit 3/7/01]<br>
